CNCP v1 22366
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#7173: Add option to enable Typescript by default in <script>",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:26.195696+00:00",
  "text": "Add option to enable Typescript by default in <script>\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\r\n\r\nIf you have fully Typescript project it doesn't make sense to write `<script lang=\"ts\">` all the time. It would be nice to have an option to enable Typescript by default.\r\n\r\n### What does the proposed API look like?\r\n\r\n```ts\r\ncompileScript(src, {\r\n  defaultLang: 'ts'\r\n})\r\n```",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request",
    "scope: compiler"
  ],
